Running command: cat > check_solution.py << 'PY'
from solution import Solution

solutions = [
    ( ["leet","code"], "e", [0,1] ),
    ( ["abc","bcd","aaaa","cbc"], "a", [0,2] ),
    ( ["abc","bcd","aaaa","cbc"], "z", [] ),
    ( ["a"], "a", [0] ),
    ( [""], "a", [] ),
    ( ["abc","def","gha"], "g", [2] ),
]

s = Solution()

for words, x, expected in solutions:
    out = s.findWordsContaining(words, x)
    # sort since order may be any
    out_sorted = sorted(out)
    if out_sorted == expected:
        print("PASS", words, x, "->", out)
    else:
        print("FAIL", words, x, "->", out, " expected:", expected)
